 from meg arnold qm sri com meg arnold subject botulinum toxin type a organization sri international lines two four distribution world nntp posting host one two eight one eight three five five zero i am looking for statistics on the prevalence of disorders that are treatable with botulinum type a these disorders include facial dyskinesia meige syndrome hemifacial spasm apraxia of eyelid openeing aberrant regeneration of the facial nerve facial paralysis strabismus spasmodic torticollis muscle spasm occupational dystonia i e writers cramp etc spasmodic dysphonia and temporal mandibular joint disease i realize many of the disorders i listed such as muscle spasm are vaguely defined and may encompass a wide range of particular disorders my apologies the list was provided to me as is i have some numbers but not reliable any ideas on sources or even bbetter any actual figures with source listed many thanks meg meg arnold business intelligence center sri international three three three ravenswood avenue menlo park ca nine four zero two five phone four one five eight five nine three seven six four internet meg arnold qm sri com